Subject: Stealthbits AIC Not Update User Reports
Description: Some groups appear in AIC, but when you search for them in ADInventoy_GroupView, they do not appear among the groups.
What_We_Know__c:
The group was part of the azure.
The Azure AD Inventory job was not set up as it should have been.
Next_Steps__c:
The customer will run a full ADI scan. 
If the full scan does not fix the issue, I will drop the domain and then rerun a full scan.
Solution_Comment__c:
We set up the Azure AD Inventory job
We ran a full Azure ADI scan
We reviewed the results from those groups under the AzureADInventoy_GroupMembersView and noticed that the removed users are no longer on the list.
We verified from the AIC, and those users were not listed.
Account_Name__c: Woodmen of the World Life Insurance Society
